snippet.title: Iron Vulture - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Iron Vulture on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/968770/Iron_Vulture/
Sign-Up for Demo Now: https://ironvulturegame.com/en/index


Iron Vulture is a real-time strategy line defender. You can command six soldiers in real-time combat, move them across lanes, and use their specialties to eliminate wave after wave of mutated creatures.

For more information:
Iron Vulture website: https://ironvulturegame.com/en/index
Discord server: https://go.ironvulturegame.com/Discord

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/IronVulture/
Website: https://ironvulturegame.com/en/index
001Sutdio on Twitter: https://twitter.com/001studios
